{"tid":797414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國中央機關及香港政府聯合宣佈香港獨立","createTime":"2018-08-28T13:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T13:28:13.000Z","uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75428c10d722b1c68d2c5660e16eff6c5bfb17d5","tid":797414,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"派身份證俾香港人為收稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中央機關為高鐵幾十蚊手續費直接搞香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017年9月27日<br />\n// 中國鐵路總司決定自2017年10月1日起，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全國鐵路取消鐵路異地票售票手續費</span></strong>，即在各火車站售票視窗、代售點視窗購買異地火車票不再加收每張5元的手續費。//<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sohu.com/a/195589323_255783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F195589323_255783&d=qVLSHLgkGmWQNFq70Z9n5f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cc565f67\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sohu.com/a/195589323_255783</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年8月16日<br />\n// 林鄭月娥昨在北京與中國鐵路總公司會面，她在會前<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公布高鐵手續費細節</strong></span>，高鐵香港段通車後，在西九總站會設5個櫃枱售賣內地段車票，若票價低於200元人民幣（約230港元），手續費10港元；售價200至299元人民幣（約230至340港元）車票，手續費20港元；售價300元人民幣（約340港元）或以上，手續費30港元。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180816/s00001/1534356591843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180816%2Fs00001%2F1534356591843&d=qVLSHLgkGmWQNFq70Z9n5f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=89a8eaa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180816%2Fs00001%2F1534356591843&h=c1bd7e93\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180816/s00001/1534356591843</a><br />\n<br />\n林奠仲要講手續費平咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n// 林太說，原定手續費為40至90元，形容今次是大幅下調 //<br />\n<br />\n但其實手續費只收香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990932c43b0bd237541c8302ce47dc0e18bca613","tid":797414,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"睇完段字,琴晚又真係發夢見到香港獨立於中國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:這裏中國是指<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中華民國</span></span>為正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152a17965d5983437b2af7f35da4ed75db5c378b","tid":797414,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"中國鐵路總公司 = 中華民國鐵路總公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}